title: Tim Mclean- The Chilling Greyhound Bus Case - Justice Served?
description:
Hi Friends!
 Hope you are having a wonderful day today so far. Today I wanted to talk about Tim Mclean and what in the world happened to him on the greyhound bus. The whole story is strange.
  I hope the family and passengers get the justice they deserve but most of all are able to heal and move forward. Love and appreciate you guys so much and I hope to be seeing you very soon
xo
Bailey Sarian
